{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Ten years ago exactly,"},{"time":2000,"text":"I was in Afghanistan."},{"time":4000,"text":"I was covering the war in Afghanistan,"},{"time":8000,"text":"and I witnessed, as a reporter for Al Jazeera,"},{"time":11000,"text":"the amount of suffering and destruction"},{"time":14000,"text":"that emerged out of a war like that."},{"time":17000,"text":"Then, two years later,"},{"time":19000,"text":"I covered another war -- the war in Iraq."},{"time":21000,"text":"I was placed at the center of that war"},{"time":24000,"text":"because I was covering the war"},{"time":26000,"text":"from the northern part of Iraq."},{"time":29000,"text":"And the war ended"},{"time":31000,"text":"with a regime change,"},{"time":33000,"text":"like the one in Afghanistan."},{"time":35000,"text":"And that regime"},{"time":37000,"text":"that we got rid of"},{"time":39000,"text":"was actually a dictatorship,"},{"time":42000,"text":"an authoritarian regime,"},{"time":44000,"text":"that for decades"},{"time":47000,"text":"created a great sense of paralysis"},{"time":51000,"text":"within the nation, within the people themselves."},{"time":54000,"text":"However,"},{"time":56000,"text":"the change that came through foreign intervention"},{"time":58000,"text":"created even worse circumstances for the people"},{"time":61000,"text":"and deepened the sense"},{"time":63000,"text":"of paralysis and inferiority"},{"time":65000,"text":"in that part of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"For decades,"},{"time":69000,"text":"we have lived under authoritarian regimes --"},{"time":72000,"text":"in the Arab world, in the Middle East."},{"time":75000,"text":"These regimes"},{"time":77000,"text":"created something within us during this period."},{"time":80000,"text":"I'm 43 years old right now."},{"time":82000,"text":"For the last 40 years,"},{"time":84000,"text":"I have seen almost the same faces"},{"time":86000,"text":"for kings and presidents ruling us --"},{"time":90000,"text":"old, aged, authoritarian,"},{"time":94000,"text":"corrupt situations --"},{"time":96000,"text":"regimes that we have seen around us."},{"time":99000,"text":"And for a moment I was wondering,"},{"time":102000,"text":"are we going to live in order to see"},{"time":104000,"text":"real change happening on the ground,"},{"time":107000,"text":"a change that does not come through foreign intervention,"},{"time":110000,"text":"through the misery of occupation,"},{"time":113000,"text":"through nations invading our land"},{"time":116000,"text":"and deepening the sense of inferiority sometimes?"},{"time":120000,"text":"The Iraqis: yes, they got rid of Saddam Hussein,"},{"time":123000,"text":"but when they saw"},{"time":125000,"text":"their land occupied by foreign forces"},{"time":128000,"text":"they felt very sad,"},{"time":130000,"text":"they felt that their dignity had suffered."},{"time":133000,"text":"And this is why they revolted."},{"time":135000,"text":"This is why they did not accept."},{"time":138000,"text":"And actually other regimes, they told their citizens,"},{"time":141000,"text":"\"Would you like to see the situation of Iraq?"},{"time":144000,"text":"Would you like to see civil war, sectarian killing?"},{"time":147000,"text":"Would you like to see destruction?"},{"time":149000,"text":"Would you like to see foreign troops on your land?\""},{"time":152000,"text":"And the people thought for themselves,"},{"time":154000,"text":"\"Maybe we should live with"},{"time":156000,"text":"this kind of authoritarian situation that we find ourselves in,"},{"time":159000,"text":"instead of having the second scenario.\""},{"time":163000,"text":"That was one of the worst nightmares that we have seen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"For 10 years,"},{"time":168000,"text":"unfortunately we have found ourselves"},{"time":170000,"text":"reporting images of destruction,"},{"time":173000,"text":"images of killing,"},{"time":175000,"text":"of sectarian conflicts,"},{"time":177000,"text":"images of violence,"},{"time":179000,"text":"emerging from a magnificent piece of land,"},{"time":182000,"text":"a region that one day was the source"},{"time":184000,"text":"of civilizations and art and culture"},{"time":187000,"text":"for thousands of years."},{"time":190000,"text":"Now I am here to tell you"},{"time":193000,"text":"that the future"},{"time":195000,"text":"that we were dreaming for"},{"time":197000,"text":"has eventually arrived."},{"time":201000,"text":"A new generation,"},{"time":203000,"text":"well-educated,"},{"time":205000,"text":"connected,"},{"time":207000,"text":"inspired by universal values"},{"time":211000,"text":"and a global understanding,"},{"time":214000,"text":"has created a new reality for us."},{"time":218000,"text":"We have found a new way"},{"time":221000,"text":"to express our feelings"},{"time":224000,"text":"and to express our dreams:"},{"time":227000,"text":"these young people"},{"time":229000,"text":"who have restored self-confidence"},{"time":231000,"text":"in our nations in that part of the world,"},{"time":234000,"text":"who have given us"},{"time":236000,"text":"new meaning for freedom"},{"time":239000,"text":"and empowered us to go down to the streets."},{"time":242000,"text":"Nothing happened. No violence. Nothing."},{"time":244000,"text":"Just step out of your house,"},{"time":246000,"text":"raise your voice"},{"time":248000,"text":"and say, \"We would like to see the end of the regime.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"This is what happened in Tunisia."},{"time":254000,"text":"Over a few days,"},{"time":256000,"text":"the Tunisian regime that invested billions of dollars"},{"time":259000,"text":"in the security agencies,"},{"time":261000,"text":"billions of dollars"},{"time":263000,"text":"in maintaining, trying to maintain,"},{"time":265000,"text":"its prisons,"},{"time":267000,"text":"collapsed, disappeared,"},{"time":269000,"text":"because of the voices of the public."},{"time":272000,"text":"People who were inspired to go down to the streets"},{"time":274000,"text":"and to raise their voices,"},{"time":276000,"text":"they tried to kill."},{"time":278000,"text":"The intelligence agencies wanted to arrest people."},{"time":281000,"text":"They found something called Facebook."},{"time":284000,"text":"They found something called Twitter."},{"time":286000,"text":"They were surprised by all of these kinds of issues."},{"time":288000,"text":"And they said,"},{"time":290000,"text":"\"These kids are misled.\""},{"time":293000,"text":"Therefore, they asked their parents"},{"time":295000,"text":"to go down to the streets"},{"time":297000,"text":"and collect them, bring them back home."},{"time":299000,"text":"This is what they were telling. This is their propaganda."},{"time":301000,"text":"\"Bring these kids home"},{"time":303000,"text":"because they are misled.\""},{"time":305000,"text":"But yes,"},{"time":307000,"text":"these youth"},{"time":309000,"text":"who have been inspired"},{"time":311000,"text":"by universal values,"},{"time":313000,"text":"who are idealistic enough"},{"time":315000,"text":"to imagine a magnificent future"},{"time":317000,"text":"and, at the same time, realistic enough"},{"time":320000,"text":"to balance this kind of imagination"},{"time":323000,"text":"and the process leading to it --"},{"time":326000,"text":"not using violence,"},{"time":328000,"text":"not trying to create chaos --"},{"time":330000,"text":"these young people,"},{"time":332000,"text":"they did not go home."},{"time":334000,"text":"Parents actually went to the streets"},{"time":336000,"text":"and they supported them."},{"time":338000,"text":"And this is how the revolution was born in Tunisia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"We in Al Jazeera"},{"time":343000,"text":"were banned from Tunisia for years,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and the government did not allow"},{"time":348000,"text":"any Al Jazeera reporter to be there."},{"time":350000,"text":"But we found that these people in the street,"},{"time":353000,"text":"all of them are our reporters,"},{"time":355000,"text":"feeding our newsroom"},{"time":357000,"text":"with pictures, with videos"},{"time":359000,"text":"and with news."},{"time":361000,"text":"And suddenly that newsroom in Doha"},{"time":364000,"text":"became a center"},{"time":366000,"text":"that received all this kind of input from ordinary people --"},{"time":369000,"text":"people who are connected and people who have ambition"},{"time":372000,"text":"and who have liberated themselves"},{"time":374000,"text":"from the feeling of inferiority."},{"time":376000,"text":"And then we took that decision:"},{"time":379000,"text":"We are unrolling the news."},{"time":381000,"text":"We are going to be the voice for these voiceless people."},{"time":384000,"text":"We are going to spread the message."},{"time":386000,"text":"Yes, some of these young people"},{"time":388000,"text":"are connected to the Internet,"},{"time":390000,"text":"but the connectivity in the Arab world"},{"time":392000,"text":"is very little, is very small,"},{"time":394000,"text":"because of many problems that we are suffering from."},{"time":397000,"text":"But Al Jazeera took the voice from these people"},{"time":400000,"text":"and we amplified [it]."},{"time":402000,"text":"We put it in every sitting room in the Arab world --"},{"time":405000,"text":"and internationally, globally,"},{"time":407000,"text":"through our English channel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"And then people started to feel"},{"time":412000,"text":"that there's something new happening."},{"time":415000,"text":"And then Zine al-Abidine Ben Ali"},{"time":418000,"text":"decided to leave."},{"time":420000,"text":"And then Egypt started,"},{"time":422000,"text":"and Hosni Mubarak decided to leave."},{"time":424000,"text":"And now Libya as you see it."},{"time":426000,"text":"And then you have Yemen."},{"time":428000,"text":"And you have many other countries trying to see"},{"time":430000,"text":"and to rediscover that feeling"},{"time":433000,"text":"of, \"How do we imagine a future"},{"time":435000,"text":"which is magnificent and peaceful and tolerant?\""},{"time":438000,"text":"I want to tell you something,"},{"time":441000,"text":"that the Internet and connectivity"},{"time":445000,"text":"has created [a] new mindset."},{"time":448000,"text":"But this mindset"},{"time":450000,"text":"has continued to be faithful"},{"time":452000,"text":"to the soil and to the land"},{"time":454000,"text":"that it emerged from."},{"time":457000,"text":"And while this was the major difference"},{"time":460000,"text":"between many initiatives before"},{"time":463000,"text":"to create change,"},{"time":465000,"text":"before we thought, and governments told us --"},{"time":467000,"text":"and even sometimes it was true --"},{"time":470000,"text":"that change was imposed on us,"},{"time":473000,"text":"and people rejected that,"},{"time":475000,"text":"because they thought that it is alien to their culture."},{"time":478000,"text":"Always, we believed"},{"time":481000,"text":"that change will spring from within,"},{"time":484000,"text":"that change should be a reconciliation"},{"time":488000,"text":"with culture, cultural diversity,"},{"time":491000,"text":"with our faith in our tradition"},{"time":493000,"text":"and in our history,"},{"time":495000,"text":"but at the same time,"},{"time":497000,"text":"open to universal values, connected with the world,"},{"time":500000,"text":"tolerant to the outside."},{"time":502000,"text":"And this is the moment"},{"time":504000,"text":"that is happening right now in the Arab world."},{"time":506000,"text":"This is the right moment, and this is the actual moment"},{"time":509000,"text":"that we see all of these meanings meet together"},{"time":511000,"text":"and then create the beginning"},{"time":513000,"text":"of this magnificent era"},{"time":515000,"text":"that will emerge from the region."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"How did the elite deal with that --"},{"time":521000,"text":"the so-called political elite?"},{"time":524000,"text":"In front of Facebook,"},{"time":527000,"text":"they brought the camels in Tahrir Square."},{"time":530000,"text":"In front of Al Jazeera,"},{"time":532000,"text":"they started creating tribalism."},{"time":536000,"text":"And then when they failed,"},{"time":538000,"text":"they started speaking about conspiracies"},{"time":541000,"text":"that emerged from Tel Aviv and Washington"},{"time":544000,"text":"in order to divide the Arab world."},{"time":547000,"text":"They started telling the West,"},{"time":549000,"text":"\"Be aware of Al-Qaeda."},{"time":551000,"text":"Al-Qaeda is taking over our territories."},{"time":553000,"text":"These are Islamists"},{"time":555000,"text":"trying to create new Imaras."},{"time":557000,"text":"Be aware of these people"},{"time":559000,"text":"who [are] coming to you"},{"time":562000,"text":"in order to ruin your great civilization.\""},{"time":565000,"text":"Fortunately,"},{"time":568000,"text":"people right now cannot be deceived."},{"time":570000,"text":"Because this corrupt elite"},{"time":573000,"text":"in that region"},{"time":575000,"text":"has lost even the power of deception."},{"time":579000,"text":"They could not, and they cannot, imagine"},{"time":581000,"text":"how they could really deal with this reality."},{"time":584000,"text":"They have lost."},{"time":586000,"text":"They have been detached"},{"time":588000,"text":"from their people, from the masses,"},{"time":591000,"text":"and now we are seeing them collapsing"},{"time":594000,"text":"one after the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"Al Jazeera is not"},{"time":600000,"text":"a tool of revolution."},{"time":602000,"text":"We do not create revolutions."},{"time":604000,"text":"However,"},{"time":606000,"text":"when something of that magnitude happens,"},{"time":609000,"text":"we are at the center of the coverage."},{"time":612000,"text":"We were banned from Egypt,"},{"time":614000,"text":"and our correspondents,"},{"time":616000,"text":"some of them were arrested."},{"time":619000,"text":"But most of our camera people"},{"time":622000,"text":"and our journalists,"},{"time":624000,"text":"they went underground in Egypt -- voluntarily --"},{"time":627000,"text":"to report what happened in Tahrir Square."},{"time":630000,"text":"For 18 days,"},{"time":632000,"text":"our cameras were broadcasting, live,"},{"time":635000,"text":"the voices of the people in Tahrir Square."},{"time":638000,"text":"I remember one night"},{"time":640000,"text":"when someone phoned me on my cellphone --"},{"time":642000,"text":"ordinary person who I don't know -- from Tahrir Square."},{"time":644000,"text":"He told me, \"We appeal to you"},{"time":646000,"text":"not to switch off the cameras."},{"time":648000,"text":"If you switch off the cameras tonight,"},{"time":650000,"text":"there will be a genocide."},{"time":652000,"text":"You are protecting us"},{"time":654000,"text":"by showing what is happening at Tahrir Square.\""},{"time":657000,"text":"I felt the responsibility"},{"time":659000,"text":"to phone our correspondents there"},{"time":661000,"text":"and to phone our newsroom"},{"time":663000,"text":"and to tell them, \"Make your best"},{"time":665000,"text":"not to switch off the cameras at night,"},{"time":667000,"text":"because the guys there really feel confident"},{"time":670000,"text":"when someone is reporting their story --"},{"time":672000,"text":"and they feel protected as well.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":675000,"text":"So we have a chance"},{"time":678000,"text":"to create a new future"},{"time":680000,"text":"in that part of the world."},{"time":682000,"text":"We have a chance"},{"time":685000,"text":"to go and to think of the future"},{"time":688000,"text":"as something which is open to the world."},{"time":691000,"text":"Let us not repeat the mistake of Iran,"},{"time":694000,"text":"of [the] Mosaddeq revolution."},{"time":696000,"text":"Let us free ourselves -- especially in the West --"},{"time":699000,"text":"from thinking about that part of the world"},{"time":701000,"text":"based on oil interest,"},{"time":704000,"text":"or based on interests"},{"time":707000,"text":"of the illusion of stability and security."},{"time":710000,"text":"The stability and security"},{"time":713000,"text":"of authoritarian regimes"},{"time":716000,"text":"cannot create"},{"time":718000,"text":"but terrorism and violence and destruction."},{"time":720000,"text":"Let us accept the choice of the people."},{"time":723000,"text":"Let us not pick and choose"},{"time":725000,"text":"who we would like to rule their future."},{"time":728000,"text":"The future should be ruled"},{"time":730000,"text":"by people themselves,"},{"time":732000,"text":"even sometimes if they are voices"},{"time":734000,"text":"that might now scare us."},{"time":736000,"text":"But the values of democracy"},{"time":739000,"text":"and the freedom of choice"},{"time":741000,"text":"that is sweeping the Middle East at this moment in time"},{"time":744000,"text":"is the best opportunity for the world,"},{"time":746000,"text":"for the West and the East,"},{"time":748000,"text":"to see stability and to see security"},{"time":751000,"text":"and to see friendship and to see tolerance"},{"time":754000,"text":"emerging from the Arab world,"},{"time":756000,"text":"rather than the images of violence and terrorism."},{"time":759000,"text":"Let us support these people."},{"time":761000,"text":"Let us stand for them."},{"time":763000,"text":"And let us give up"},{"time":765000,"text":"our narrow selfishness"},{"time":768000,"text":"in order to embrace change,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and in order to celebrate with the people of that region"},{"time":773000,"text":"a great future"},{"time":775000,"text":"and hope and tolerance."},{"time":778000,"text":"The future has arrived,"},{"time":780000,"text":"and the future is now."},{"time":782000,"text":"I thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":804000,"text":"Chris Anderson: I just have a couple of questions for you."},{"time":806000,"text":"Thank you for coming here."},{"time":808000,"text":"How would you characterize the historical significance"},{"time":810000,"text":"of what's happened?"},{"time":812000,"text":"Is this a story-of-the-year, a story-of-the-decade"},{"time":815000,"text":"or something more?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":817000,"text":"Wadah Khanfar: Actually, this may be the biggest story that we have ever covered."},{"time":820000,"text":"We have covered many wars."},{"time":822000,"text":"We have covered a lot of tragedies, a lot of problems,"},{"time":824000,"text":"a lot of conflict zones, a lot of hot spots in the region,"},{"time":827000,"text":"because we were centered at the middle of it."},{"time":829000,"text":"But this is a story -- it is a great story; it is beautiful."},{"time":833000,"text":"It is not something that you only cover"},{"time":836000,"text":"because you have to cover a great incident."},{"time":839000,"text":"You are witnessing change in history."},{"time":842000,"text":"You are witnessing the birth of a new era."},{"time":845000,"text":"And this is what the story's all about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":847000,"text":"CA: There are a lot of people in the West"},{"time":849000,"text":"who are still skeptical,"},{"time":851000,"text":"or think this may just be an intermediate stage"},{"time":854000,"text":"before much more alarming chaos."},{"time":857000,"text":"You really believe"},{"time":859000,"text":"that if there are democratic elections in Egypt now,"},{"time":862000,"text":"that a government could emerge"},{"time":864000,"text":"that espouses some of the values you've spoken about so inspiringly?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"WK: And people actually,"},{"time":869000,"text":"after the collapse of the Hosni Mubarak regime,"},{"time":872000,"text":"the youth who have organized themselves"},{"time":874000,"text":"in certain groups and councils,"},{"time":877000,"text":"they are guarding the transformation"},{"time":880000,"text":"and they are trying to put it on a track"},{"time":882000,"text":"in order to satisfy"},{"time":884000,"text":"the values of democracy,"},{"time":886000,"text":"but at the same time"},{"time":888000,"text":"also to make it reasonable"},{"time":890000,"text":"and to make it rational,"},{"time":892000,"text":"not to go out of order."},{"time":895000,"text":"In my opinion, these people are much more wiser"},{"time":898000,"text":"than, not only the political elite,"},{"time":900000,"text":"even the intellectual elite, even opposition leaders"},{"time":903000,"text":"including political parties."},{"time":905000,"text":"At this moment in time, the youth in the Arab world"},{"time":908000,"text":"are much more wiser"},{"time":910000,"text":"and capable of creating the change"},{"time":912000,"text":"than the old --"},{"time":914000,"text":"including the political and cultural"},{"time":916000,"text":"and ideological"},{"time":918000,"text":"old regimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":920000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":923000,"text":"CA: We are not to get involved politically and interfere in that way."},{"time":926000,"text":"What should people here at TED,"},{"time":929000,"text":"here in the West,"},{"time":931000,"text":"do if they want to connect or make a difference"},{"time":934000,"text":"and they believe in what's happening here?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":936000,"text":"WK: I think we have discovered a very important issue in the Arab world --"},{"time":938000,"text":"that people care,"},{"time":940000,"text":"people care about this great transformation."},{"time":943000,"text":"Mohamed Nanabhay who's sitting with us,"},{"time":945000,"text":"the head of Aljazeera.net,"},{"time":948000,"text":"he told me that a 2,500 percent increase"},{"time":953000,"text":"of accessing our website"},{"time":955000,"text":"from various parts of the world."},{"time":957000,"text":"Fifty percent of it is coming from America."},{"time":959000,"text":"Because we discovered that people care,"},{"time":961000,"text":"and people would like to know --"},{"time":963000,"text":"they are receiving the stream through our Internet."},{"time":966000,"text":"Unfortunately in the United States,"},{"time":968000,"text":"we are not covering but Washington D.C. at this moment in time"},{"time":971000,"text":"for Al Jazeera English."},{"time":973000,"text":"But I can tell you, this is the moment to celebrate"},{"time":976000,"text":"through connecting ourselves"},{"time":978000,"text":"with those people in the street"},{"time":980000,"text":"and expressing our support to them"},{"time":983000,"text":"and expressing this kind of feeling, universal feeling,"},{"time":987000,"text":"of supporting the weak and the oppressed"},{"time":990000,"text":"to create a much better future for all of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":993000,"text":"CA: Well Wadah, a group of members of the TED community,"},{"time":996000,"text":"TEDxCairo,"},{"time":998000,"text":"are meeting as we speak."},{"time":1000000,"text":"They've had some speakers there."},{"time":1002000,"text":"I believe they've heard your talk."},{"time":1004000,"text":"Thank you for inspiring them and for inspiring all of us."},{"time":1006000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}